WEBVTT

00:01.364 --> 00:07.851
And all of us in a group would walk wherever the 
party was. For instance, one night we met down here

00:07.871 --> 00:28.772
on Texas Avenue, I guess that's about 33rd Street, 
and walked out to home, not down by where I was born,

00:07.871 --> 00:28.772
a couple of blocks beyond, in a group. And then we 
all walked back to that same house and then made it

00:30.035 --> 00:40.968
around the very home where the girl lived. It 
wasn't any of them to spend the night. I was

00:43.991 --> 00:45.993
accustomed with that girl. I usually met her at the 
girl's

00:46.093 --> 00:50.098
house. And we always had a class party every year in 
school, grade school. different homes around,

01:01.253 --> 01:07.839
but I was there, of course, they were afternoon 
parties. How about birthday parties, Mac, in

01:07.859 --> 01:09.621
those days? Was that just a family affair, or would 
you have... No, they'd have big men, big birthday

01:09.661 --> 01:15.186
parties. That was a big thing.

01:19.190 --> 01:28.999
And, uh...

01:19.190 --> 01:28.999
Yeah, a dancing teacher came in, set up a class, I 
guess that was long, about 1913. That was the first

01:32.452 --> 01:41.242
one I ever heard

01:32.452 --> 01:41.242
of. My mother put me in the class.

01:45.728 --> 01:48.611
I was the only boy, about 14 girls. Well,

01:48.631 --> 01:52.876
did you enjoy it? Hell no. She whipped me every day 
before I agreed to go. Sometimes you'd have to

02:00.772 --> 02:06.360
crawl along. But they was a girl just about right 
for me, and they paired us. And I felt sorry for her

02:15.011 --> 02:22.341
because she had to dance with me every class, the 
whole thing. No changing around. Of course, what

02:24.211 --> 02:35.687
we enjoyed most in those days, they had a skating 
rink way down on Washington Street.

02:35.707 --> 02:36.929
That was a real attraction. We enjoyed that much 
more than trying to dance. We started at that

02:43.157 --> 02:52.210
maybe, well, I guess I was five years old when I 
started going there to skate. And it continued,

02:52.966 --> 02:57.972
and lots of grown people, all ages. My mother was a 
wonderful skater. Did they have shoe skates in

03:01.476 --> 03:04.199
those days? Yeah. The whole unit together, or just 
the clamp-ons? They had them. Oh, they clamped on.

03:09.585 --> 03:11.047
That was the only kind they had. Oh. Well, those 
others, they had the ice skates. Well, they have

03:17.815 --> 03:21.119
some roller skate now that are the shoe and 
everything all together. Well, it's been so long.

03:23.240 --> 03:25.503
The tees, they fit you. You wore you right in the 
shoes.

03:32.411 --> 03:35.175
My mother, as I say, was a wonderful skater. My 
father was clubbed in his hands. He didn't bust his

03:42.083 --> 03:43.845
ass. What are you talking about? That's all right. 
Why he didn't break himself, all the pieces, I'll

03:46.188 --> 03:51.795
never know. But all ages can.

