Well, the Lawrence family seems to have stayed in a 
pretty high position of affluence throughout. I

09:27.906 --> 09:30.710
don't know much about the Howells. The Howells? 
The Howell family you mentioned? I'm not sure

09:32.371 --> 09:33.733
about it. Well, no, actually, the Lawrence family 
