09:35.536 --> 09:48.374
hell, always in a bind. The Howells were the 
richest family in the Bronx. They owned

09:53.882 --> 09:57.106
everything. They even got into retail grocery 
business. And then... They got into wholesale

10:03.903 --> 10:07.728
grocery business. Howling Company did every bit 
as much, maybe a little more business than

10:07.748 --> 10:14.878
Lawrence Grocers Company. And that was just one of 
their interests. Lawrence Grocers Company, that

10:20.887 --> 10:27.476
was my father's main interest, almost. Well, he 
