not quite that many. Well? In fact, he never did 
acquire control in his own name, but in the 20s,

11:09.091 --> 11:13.117
I wanted to sell his stock. My father recommended 
that I buy it, and I did. That gave us control of the

11:17.943 --> 11:22.089
two of us. Well, we had $102,000 worth of stock and 
$200,000 worth of corporation. That's the

11:30.321 --> 11:31.683
control we had. The Howells had nobody else 
interested in the family. the old gentleman and

11:37.863 --> 11:42.729
his three sons. What's happened to the Howell 
family since then? Well, they've all died out, and

11:45.432 --> 12:05.777
the only one who has left married a Navasota girl, 
and he moved down there and operated the

11:45.432 --> 12:05.777
lumberyard down there for a long time. sold his 
interest down there and then moved back here. But

12:10.058 --> 12:14.544
he's always been retired. Now, he's an unusually 
well-fixed man himself. He inherited a lot of

12:22.174 --> 12:24.257
money. He made a lot of money. But his wife was four 
more than he is. She's now a soldier. Her father was

12:32.808 --> 12:35.932
a doctor down there. He made a hell of a lot of money 
and died. Her mother. Is this going on the record?

