22:05.393 --> 22:14.886
give to him to succeed in life and to, as well as 
economically, just to be a good person and a good

22:05.393 --> 22:14.886
citizen? I tell you, I told my children and 
grandchildren, first, keep the very best company

22:17.029 --> 22:25.521
possible. Second, choose a worthy objective, a 
challenge. Third, work at it hard. and live for the

22:35.313 --> 22:37.976
best things in life. Well, that seems like mighty 
fine advice. Well, it is the best I ever was, even if

22:40.598 --> 22:47.245
it isn't mine. Well, John, is there anything that 
you can think that you'd like to take that you might

22:47.265 --> 23:01.118
be especially interested in other people hearing 
about?

